          "step": 16,
          "text": "Install camshaft, camshaft brackets and distributor bracket. Tighten camshaft bracket bolts gradually in three stages:\n(a) 2 N\u00b7m (0.2 kg-m, 1 ft-lb)\n(b) 5.9 N\u00b7m (0.6 kg-m, 4 ft-lb)\n(c) 9 - 12 N\u00b7m (0.9 - 1.2 kg-m, 6 - 9 ft-lb)",
